    "excerpt": "The prayer for King George III in the English colonies before the Revolutionary War. . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nהַנּוֹתֵן תְּשׁוּעָה לַמְּלָכִים<br />\nוּמֶמְשָׁלָה לַנְּסִיכִים<br />\nמַלְכוּתוֹ מַלְכוּת כׇּל־עוֹלָמִים<br />\nהַפּוֹצֶה אֶת דָּוִד עַבְדּוֹ מֵחֶרֶב רָעָה<br />\nהַנּוֹתֵן בַּיַם דֶרֶךְ<br />\nוּבְמַיִם עַזִּים נְתִיבָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nMay he that dispenseth Salvation unto Kings,<br />\nand Dominion unto Princes;<br />\nwhose Kingdom is an everlasting Kingdom;<br />\nthat delivered his Servant David from the destructive Sword;<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find 1 Chronicles 21:15.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nthat maketh a Way in the Sea,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> i.e., for the Israelites through the Sea of Reeds.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nand a Path through the mighty Waters:<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> again, for the Israelites, through the River Jordan.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nהוּא יְבָרֵךְ וְיִשְׁמוֹר וְיִנְצוֹר וְיַעֲזוֹר<br />\nלַאֲדוֹנֵנוּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nBless, preserve, guard, and assist,<br />\nour most gracious Sovereign Lord,<br />\nKing George [III],<br />\nour gracious Queen Charlotte,<br />\ntheir Royal Highnesses George Prince of Wales,<br />\nthe Princess Dowager of Wales,<br />\nand all the Royal Family.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> In the Colonies, after the King and Royal Family, the Governor and Magistrates, are added.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nמֶֽלֶךְ מַלְכֵי הַמְּלָכִים<br />\nבְּרַחֲמָיו יְחַיֵֽהוּ<br />\nוְיִשְׁמְרֵֽהוּ וּמִכׇּל צָרָה וְיָגוֹן וָנֶֽזֶק יַצִּילֵה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nMay the supreme King of Kings,<br />\nthrough his infinite Mercies preserve them, and grant them Life<br />\nand deliver them from all Manner of Trouble and Danger.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nמֶֽלֶךְ מַלְכֵי הַמְלָכִים<br />\nיָרוּם וְיַגְבִּיהַ לַאֲדוֹנֵנוּ<br />\nוְיַאֲרִיךְ יָמִים עַל מַמְלָכְתּוֹ׃<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nMay the supreme King of Kings<br />\naggrandize and highly exalt our Sovereign Lord the King,<br />\nand grant him long and prosperously to reign.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nמֶֽלֶךְ מַלְכֵי הַמְּלָכִים בְּרַחֲמָיו יִתֵּן בְּלִבּוֹ<br />\nוּבְלֵב כׇּל יוֹעֲצָיו וְשָׂרָיו<br />\nרַחֲמָנוֹת לַעֲשׂוֹת טוֹבָה עִמָּֽנוּ<br />\nוְעִם כׇּל יִשְׂרָאֵל<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nMay the supreme King of Kings inspire him,<br />\nand his Council, and the States of his Kingdoms,<br />\nwith Benevolence towards us,<br />\nand all Israel, our Brethren.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\">\nבְּיָמָיו וּבְיָמֵֽינוּ<br />\nתִּוָּשַׁע יְהוּדָה<br />\nוְיִשְׂרָאֵל יִשְׁכּוֹן לָבֶטַח<br />\nוּבָא לְצִיּוֹן גּוֹאֵל<br />\nוְכֵן יְהִי רָצוֹן<br />\nוָנֺאמַר אָמֵן׃<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\">\nIn his, and our Days,<br />\nmay Jehudah be saved,<br />\nand Israel dwell in Safety:<br />\nAnd may the Redeemer come unto Tzion:<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Heb. And so may it be acceptable.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nWhich God of his infinite Mercies grant;<br />\nand let us say. <em>Amen</em>.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>This adaptation of the text of the prayer &#8220;haNotén Teshuah&#8221; for King George III appears in English translation on page 20 of Isaac Pinto&#8217;s <em><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=33113\">Prayers for Shabbath, Rosh-Hashanah, and [Yom] Kippur</a></em> (1766). Hebrew reconstructed from the English translation by Aharon Varady.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<style>\n       .errordiv { padding:10px; margin:10px; border: 1px solid #555555;color: #000000;background-color: #f8f8f8; width:500px; }#adva